issues.description: Input field has no accessible label. Element: <input type="checkbox">
reproSteps: Use screen reader or accessibility tools
Observe: Input has no accessible label
issues.expectedBehavior: Input should have an accessible label via <label>, aria-label, or aria-labelledby
issues.actualBehavior: Input has no accessible name for assistive technologies
issues.suggestedFix: Add a <label for="..."> element or aria-label attribute to: input
